      "description": "Third wave of GlassWorm supply chain attacks. Compromised VS Code extensions published Jan 30, 2026 under account 'oorzc'. Uses Solana wallet BjVeAjPrSKFiingBn4vZvghsGj9KCE8AJVtbc9S8o8SC for C2 address distribution. 7 C2 IPs rotated across 3.5 months. Campaign UUID: 7c102363-8542-459f-95dd-d845ec5df44c.",
